{"HAFFLE":[{"def":"To stammer; to speak unintelligibly; to prevaricate.","pos":""}],"HAFT":[{"def":"A handle; that part of an instrument or vessel taken into the hand, and by which it is held and used; -- said chiefly of a knife, sword, or dagger; the hilt.","pos":""}],"HAFTER":[{"def":"A caviler; a wrangler.","pos":""}]}